{"tid":497781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維修電腦被置入偷拍軟件，19歲大陸女生宿舍更衣被直播","createTime":"2017-12-13T06:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T09:54:55.000Z","uid":10958,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"249112087498d707b0e1c2daf3f32a35e1b71f4b","tid":497781,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:54:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>維修電腦被置入偷拍軟件，19歲大陸女生宿舍更衣被直播</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/z5KuV.34xl2Nm5HNd9WGNA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9NDIw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thenewslens/163f7c57eb0ecc4dcef64f4046f28b61\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fz5KuV.34xl2Nm5HNd9WGNA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9NDIw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthenewslens%2F163f7c57eb0ecc4dcef64f4046f28b61&h=72b5440b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">維修電腦被置入偷拍軟件，19歲大陸女生宿舍更衣被直播</span><br />\n<br />\n文：周雪君<br />\n<br />\n一名留學海外的19歲大連女生，筆記本電腦被人置入偷拍軟件，在大約兩個月內，宿舍的生活細節，包括室友更衣的情況都被偷拍，甚至直播。<br />\n<br />\n大陸媒體報道，留學海外的19歲大連女生肖婷，在國慶假期期間回大連同家人共聚，因為筆記本電腦故障，找人維修，期間被人置入偷拍軟件，肖婷未有覺察異樣，假期結束後把電腦拿回校，她在12月6日接到大陸民警電話，告知其一舉一動都被偷拍了。身在海外的肖婷起初以為是騙局，得知自己近兩個月來被偷拍甚至直播，感到驚訝、屈辱和憤怒。她返回大陸協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n她的電腦被人安裝了偷拍軟件，可以遠程控制電腦攝像鏡頭，警方向肖婷提供了4條視頻片段，當中包括宿舍的生活、室友換衣等情景被偷拍、直播。<br />\n<br />\n民警已拘捕電腦涉案維修工程師，報道指受害女孩不止一人。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述電腦專家指，不用攝像鏡頭時，最好把鏡頭遮好，筆記本電腦不用就合上。同時要及時更新保安軟件，修復漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>這篇文章來自</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4watEgYk18qFV45RvN4Ryw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9ODk-/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thenewslens/9c3880b6e4efdd69ef699892cc2cc0a6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4watEgYk18qFV45RvN4Ryw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9ODk-%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthenewslens%2F9c3880b6e4efdd69ef699892cc2cc0a6&h=b1e5a235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E8%A2%AB%E7%BD%AE%E5%85%A5%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6-19%E6%AD%B2%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E6%9B%B4%E8%A1%A3%E8%A2%AB%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-044318783.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%258B%258D%25E8%25BB%259F%25E4%25BB%25B6-19%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%258D%25E6%259B%25B4%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD-044318783.html&d=73bTbcxjpI%2Fr7VMQknwB%2F%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d10630c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%AD%E4%BF%AE%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E8%A2%AB%E7%BD%AE%E5%85%A5%E5%81%B7%E6%8B%8D%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6-19%E6%AD%B2%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E6%9B%B4%E8%A1%A3%E8%A2%AB%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-044318783.html</a>"},{"pid":"c6a438a86ec5d9838ac4af14a3eddb84bd305c15","tid":497781,"uid":36316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:06:29.000Z","msg":"我第一個屌你老母呀"},{"pid":"ef9d7de35a597c95cdc5b2a5564bd9297abec1f2","tid":497781,"uid":18366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:19:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51bae8f3e5717309984f00fe75041c6a34e304d0","tid":497781,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"網上瘋傳？"},{"pid":"17655372d49570689d888ad7ee338a043af57ff7","tid":497781,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"大陸真係咩都夠膽"},{"pid":"2b8546e7dc266ac0fb0e36052c5b758d252a9077","tid":497781,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T09:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>網上瘋傳？</blockqu